txt.en: 'I call you to my aid. Drive these curs from Barad Gúlaran!'
'Welcome, welcome to Barad Gúlaran. I wish I could be a more gracious host.'
'Enough! Come, brethren, and bolster my strength! Destroy this enemy!'
'Our army will arise, and Eriador will fall to the Shadow of Angmar!'
'Fools! Your bones will be consumed in the fire and shadow!'
'Your lives are forfeit!'
'Intruders! Your lives are forfeit. I will see you fed to the Regmyl!'
'Such insolence... driving me back into the light.'
'You cannot stand before my full might!'
'I shall need to teach you some manners!'
Arcade Portcullis
'You... we are doomed! The Rogmul will break his bonds, and we will all perish.'
'Enough! Flames unbind me. Shield me from the Light!'
'Our army will arise! Angmar will arise! All will be cast into shadow!'
'Come, brethren, come forth from the shadows and smite these fools!'
Summoning Chamber
'To arms! We are beset by the enemy!'
'Nay... if you are here, then you have the staff!'
'If you have the staff, then you must die! Without it, the Rogmul will be unbound!'
'What insolence is this? You do not belong in these halls!'
'Cease the summoning! We must retrieve the staff, else we are all doomed! Attack!'
'My power grows!'
'Sadly, I am bidden by my master to destroy you.'
'Quickly fools, the Rogmul comes. We must enforce our will....'
'Shall we begin?'
'...and assist its minions with your destruction! Darkness will consume you!'
